  TranslationSample(source: 'Siso\'s depictions of land, water center new gallery exhibition', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['西索画作成为新画廊展览的焦点']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"People Swimming in the Swimming Pool" from 2022 is one Vicente Siso artwork that will display at Tierra del Sol Gallery beginning Jan. 13. (photo courtesy of Vicente Siso)', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['2022年的《泳池戏水》是维森特·西索的又一作品，将于1月13日开始在Tierra del Sol画廊展出。（照片由维森特·西索提供）']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Tierra del Sol is pleased to present "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" at the new gallery location in West Hollywood. Siso has been an artist in the Studio Arts Program since 2012, this marks his debut solo exhibition. Siso was born 1962 in Madrid and raised between Venezuela, Trinidad and Miami; he moved with his family to Southern California in his early 20s.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['Tierra del Sol很高兴在西好莱坞新画廊展出“维森特·西索：水与陆的记忆”。西索自2012年起成为工作室艺术项目的艺术家，这是他首次举办个展。西索于1962年出生在马德里，在委内瑞拉、特立尼达和迈阿密长大，20岁左右随家人移居南加州。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Masterfully working across subject matter, Siso has generated a prolific series of landscapes, portraits, and still-life works rendered in either acrylic, pastel, pencil or watercolor. Drawing from family portraits, his own reference photographs, and recollection, his colorful compositions demonstrate his range of interests and skill across media. Siso\'s tropical landscapes and seascapes reflect the geographies of his past, employing rich patterns and incorporating people to make meaningful connections between culture, memory and the environment. Siso titles his artworks in a mix of Spanish and English, signifying the celebrated and integral complexities of his life in Los Angeles County. "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" opens on Saturday, Jan. 13, with a reception from 6-8 p.m. The exhibition is on view through Sunday, March 3.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['西索熟练掌握各种画风，用丙烯颜料、蜡笔、铅笔或水彩创作了一系列的风景、肖像和静物作品。他从家庭照、参考照片和回忆中汲取灵感，通过丰富多彩的构图展现自己的兴趣范围和跨媒介技能。西索的热带风景画和海景画复原过去的地理面貌，运用了丰富的构图，让人物融入其中，在文化、记忆和环境之间建立了有意义的联系。西索画作名称混杂着西班牙语和英语，象征着他在洛杉矶县的生活精彩又跌宕《维森特·西索：水与陆的记忆》将于1月13日（周六）开展，展览时间为晚上6-8点。展览将持续到3月3日（周日）。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The Tierra del Sol Gallery is located at 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. For information, visit tierradelsolgallery.org.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['Tierra del Sol画廊位于圣莫尼卡大道7414号。如需了解更多信息，请访问tierradelsolgallery.org。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Adapt the old, accommodate the new to solve issue', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['适应旧的，容纳新的，积极解决问题']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'At the precinct level, we just need to look at the Sydney CBD as an example of an area which has grown from its pre-settlement landscape into a two-storey city, from a maximum height of 150 feet to the soaring towers of today. At a much scaled-down level, the same can occur across Sydney\'s town centres located around transport nodes. Inner suburbs must also evolve, with a swing to more affordable apartment living at heights below the tree tops on key sites. Of course, the new growth in housing needs to be well-designed and trees, landscaping and parks need to be included along with other essential infrastructure.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['在区域层面，我们只需要以悉尼中央商务区为例，该地区已经从定居前的地貌发展成为一个两层楼高的城市，原来的高度最高150英尺，现在有了高耸入云的塔楼。在更小的层面上，同样的情况也可能发生在位于交通枢纽周围的悉尼城镇中心。近郊也必须发展起来，在关键地块树顶以下的高度，建设更经济实惠的公寓。当然，新住房开发必须经过精心设计，必须综合考虑树木、景观和公园以及其他必要的基础设施。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Our planning system also needs to adapt so that planners in suburban councils, who seem to be less supportive of change, are not the only determinants of the future shape of their suburbs. A way forward could be to have an independent decision-making body that championed quality design as long as it fitted below the tree tops and incorporated family living, large balconies, common gardens and presented a friendly appearance. This could be a role for the current NSW government architect working within a carefully crafted complying code.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['我们的规划体系也需要调整，使郊区议会的规划者（他们似乎不太支持变革）不再是决定郊区未来形态的唯一人选。未来发展方向可能是建立独立的决策机构，只要高度在树顶以下，融入家庭生活、大阳台、公共花园，并呈现出友好外观，就可以倡导优质设计。这可能是当前新南威尔士州政府建筑师在精心制定的合规规范中发挥的作用。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Over the past decade, our lives have changed through technology, with many working from home, and Sydney has gained an impressive network of metro and light rail systems. Our ability to purchase online has changed the way we shop, and friends and family seem closer because of smartphone communication. All of these adaptations from one system to another can also occur in our built environment through a planning focus on adaptive reuse rather than preferencing heritage preservation.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['在过去的十年里，科技改变了生活，许多人在家工作，悉尼拥有了令人印象深刻的地铁和轻轨系统网络。网购能力改变了人们的购物方式，朋友和家人也因为智能手机通讯而显得更加亲密。如果将规划重点放在活化再利用而不是优先考虑遗产保护，从一个系统到另一个系统的所有这些适应也可能发生在我们的建筑环境。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Chris Johnson is a former NSW government architect (1995-2005) and executive director, NSW Department of Planning (2005-2009). He was CEO of Urban Taskforce Australia between 2011 and 2019.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['克里斯·约翰逊曾任新南威尔士州政府建筑师（1995-2005年）和新南威尔士州规划部执行主任（2005-2009年）。2011年至2019年，他曾担任澳大利亚城市特别工作组的首席执行官。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'A final push for female equality', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['为女性平等做最后一搏']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Last year, the World Economic Forum forecast that it would take five generations to achieve gender equality in every nation. Now the World Bank wants to rapidly accelerate that time frame.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['去年，世界经济论坛预测，每个国家都需要五代人的努力才能实现性别平等。现在，世界银行希望迅速加快这一进程。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The international financial institution is poised to launch a strategy aimed at significantly advancing the rights and economic opportunities for girls and women by 2030. The plan focuses on improving inclusivity and resilience through access to finance, technological innovation, and changes in public policy and law.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['世界银行准备推出一项战略，旨在到2030年大幅提升女童和妇女的权利和经济机会。该计划的重点是通过获得资金、技术创新以及公共政策和法律修订，提高包容性和复原力。']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"Recent research demonstrates that both social norms and mindsets can change, for example, that engaging men and boys can foster their support and buy-in for gender equality," a consultative draft of the plan states. "Positive gender outcomes can be accelerated and scaled with a better understanding of ... how social norms and mindsets shape everyday expectations, priorities, and practices."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['“最近的研究表明，社会规范和思维方式都可以改变，例如让男性和男孩参与进来，就可以促进他们对性别平等的支持和认同，”该计划的一份咨询草案指出：“通过更好地了解……社会规范和思维方式如何影响日常期望、优先事项和行为方式，可以加快和扩大积极的性别平等成果。”']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Shifts in thought are harder to quantify than bank loans for rural women or school enrollment for girls. Yet there is plenty of evidence that female agency can move mountains. In Iran, for example, women have led the greatest threat to the Islamic government in 40 years simply by refusing to comply with laws that force them to cover their hair. In some of the 130 countries with minimum quotas for female representation in government, such as India, male resistance to female voting and political activism has eased.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['与向农村妇女提供银行贷款或提高女童入学率相比，思维方式的转变更难量化。但有大量证据表明，女性能发挥巨大作用。以伊朗为例，妇女仅仅因为拒绝遵守强制她们佩戴头巾的法律，就对伊斯兰政府构成了40年来最大的威胁。从全球范围来看，在印度等130个规定女性在政府中最低代表人数的国家中，男性对女性投票和参与政治活动的抵制有所缓解。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'In some rural African communities, civil society organizations are replacing a harmful rite of passage with health education. One such program helped Kamanda Timayio, leader of the Masai village of Maparasha, Kenya, change his mind about female genital mutilation. He told Le Monde that he had "emerged from ignorance" and would abandon the practice.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['在一些非洲农村社区，民间社会组织正开展健康教育，旨在取代有害的成年仪式。在其中一个项目的帮助下，肯尼亚马帕拉沙马赛村的领导人卡曼达·蒂马约改变了对切割女性生殖器官的看法。他告诉《世界报》，他已经“摆脱了无知”，放弃了这种做法。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank cites other examples. From 1970 to 2022, Bangladesh quadrupled female literacy rates and doubled female participation in the labor force. Its gross domestic product more than tripled. The change gathered its own momentum. Recruiting salaried women as teachers and health workers from within their own communities boosted trust "and made women\'s mobility and work more socially acceptable."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['世界银行还列举了其他例子。从1970年到2022年，孟加拉国女性识字率翻了两番，劳动力参与率翻了一番。孟加拉国国内生产总值增长了两倍多。这种变化积聚了动力。社区女性有机会担任教师和医疗人员，领取薪水，从而增强了信任，“并使女性的流动性和工作更容易被社会接受。”']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The bank\'s plan would target norms and institutions that may still require generational shifts. It has taken Rwanda more than two decades to establish itself as a model for land reforms that boost economic empowerment for women."No one benefits if women are held back," Rwanda President Paul Kagame said, arguing for land reform in 2015. "We have to change mindsets, not just the laws."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['世界银行的计划适用于可能仍需要代际变革的规范和制度。卢旺达花了二十多年时间，才增强妇女的经济权能，将自己打造成土地改革的典范。卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅在2015年主张土地改革时表示：“如果妇女受到阻碍，没有人会受益。我们必须改变观念，而不仅仅是法律。”']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank hopes to spread that message.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['世界银行希望传播这一理念。']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'German farmers and train drivers are scaring Germany\'s bosses', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Chinese', references: ['德国农民和火车司机正在吓唬德国的老板']),
];

const List<TranslationSample> enToFr_frDataset = [
  TranslationSample(source: 'Siso\'s depictions of land, water center new gallery exhibition', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Nouvelle exposition des travaux de Siso articulés autour de la terre et de l\'eau']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"People Swimming in the Swimming Pool" from 2022 is one Vicente Siso artwork that will display at Tierra del Sol Gallery beginning Jan. 13. (photo courtesy of Vicente Siso)', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Parmi les travaux de Vicente Siso se trouve une peinture datant de 2022, qui présente des personnes en train de nager dans une piscine ; cet objet d\'art sera mis à la disposition du grand public dans la galerie Tierra del Sol à partir du 13 janvier (avec l\'autorisation de Vicente Siso)']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Tierra del Sol is pleased to present "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" at the new gallery location in West Hollywood. Siso has been an artist in the Studio Arts Program since 2012, this marks his debut solo exhibition. Siso was born 1962 in Madrid and raised between Venezuela, Trinidad and Miami; he moved with his family to Southern California in his early 20s.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['La galerie Tierra del Sol a le plaisir de vous présenter l\'exposition "Vicente Siso : souvenirs de la terre et de l\'eau" exposée dans la toute nouvelle galerie située à l\'Ouest d\'Hollywood. Siso est membre du programme des arts plastiques depuis 2012. Ainsi, cet évènement marque le début de sa carrière individuelle. L\'artiste est né en 1962 à Madrid, puis a vécu dans plusieurs coins du monde, notamment au Venezuela, à Trinidad et à Miami. Par la suite, Siso s\'est installé en Californie du Sud avec sa famille à l\'aube de ses 20 ans.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Masterfully working across subject matter, Siso has generated a prolific series of landscapes, portraits, and still-life works rendered in either acrylic, pastel, pencil or watercolor. Drawing from family portraits, his own reference photographs, and recollection, his colorful compositions demonstrate his range of interests and skill across media. Siso\'s tropical landscapes and seascapes reflect the geographies of his past, employing rich patterns and incorporating people to make meaningful connections between culture, memory and the environment. Siso titles his artworks in a mix of Spanish and English, signifying the celebrated and integral complexities of his life in Los Angeles County. "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" opens on Saturday, Jan. 13, with a reception from 6-8 p.m. The exhibition is on view through Sunday, March 3.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Pointilleux dans tous ses travaux, Siso a produit une palette de réalisations représentant des paysages, des portraits, de l\'art relevant du passé, et au moyen de la peinture acrylique, du pastel, du pinceau et de l\'aquarelle. Ses compositions riches en couleurs traduisent l\'étendue de ses centres d\'intérêt, ainsi que ses aptitudes transversales, car l\'artiste s\'inspire aussi bien des portraits de famille, de ses propres photos de référence que de ses collections. Les paysages tropicaux, y compris marins peints par Siso, sont à l\'image de la dimension géographique de son passé, puisqu\'il y convoque des volets riches de sens, qui n\'excluent pas la personne humaine à l\'effet de créer des rapports éloquents entre la culture, le souvenir et l\'environnement. Pour donner un titre à ses travaux, Siso fait usage à la fois de l\'espagnol et de l\'anglais, ce qui laisserait présager une volonté manifeste de célébrer avec vigueur les complexités de sa vie dans le comté de Los Angeles. L\'exposition "Vicente Siso : souvenirs de la terre et de l\'eau" ouvre ses portes le samedi 13 janvier, par un gala qui se tiendra de 18 heures à 20 heures. Par ailleurs, l\'exposition se referme le dimanche 3 mars.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The Tierra del Sol Gallery is located at 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. For information, visit tierradelsolgallery.org.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['La galerie Tierra del Sol se trouve au 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. Pour plus d\'informations, veuillez visiter le site : tierradelsolgallery.org.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Adapt the old, accommodate the new to solve issue', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Adapter l\'ancien, accueillir le nouveau et apporter des solutions']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'At the precinct level, we just need to look at the Sydney CBD as an example of an area which has grown from its pre-settlement landscape into a two-storey city, from a maximum height of 150 feet to the soaring towers of today. At a much scaled-down level, the same can occur across Sydney\'s town centres located around transport nodes. Inner suburbs must also evolve, with a swing to more affordable apartment living at heights below the tree tops on key sites. Of course, the new growth in housing needs to be well-designed and trees, landscaping and parks need to be included along with other essential infrastructure.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Au niveau de la circonscription, il suffit d\'observer le centre d\'affaires de Sydney, qui pourrait servir d\'illustration de zones ayant progressé de leur état précolonial à une ville à deux étages, de bâtiments de 150 pieds maximum aux tours que nous voyons émerger à ce jour. Sur un échelon plus bas, le parallèle demeure, si l\'on considère les centres-villes de Sydney près des réseaux de transport. Les banlieues reculées doivent également connaitre le développement, en proposant des appartements locatifs à des coûts plus abordables en-deçà des pics des sites de premier plan. Il va s\'en dire que la croissance nouvellement enregistrée sur le marché de l\'immobilier doit être encadrée, notamment en ce qui concerne les arbres et l\'attractivité des paysages et des parcs, qui doivent compter parmi les infrastructures de base.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Our planning system also needs to adapt so that planners in suburban councils, who seem to be less supportive of change, are not the only determinants of the future shape of their suburbs. A way forward could be to have an independent decision-making body that championed quality design as long as it fitted below the tree tops and incorporated family living, large balconies, common gardens and presented a friendly appearance. This could be a role for the current NSW government architect working within a carefully crafted complying code.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['En outre, nous devons améliorer notre système de planification, afin que les mairies des banlieues, qui semblent les plus réfractaires au changement, ne soient pas les seules actrices de la future configuration de leurs banlieues respectives. La mise sur pied d\'un organe de décision composé d\'experts en planification proposant des offres en-deçà des pics des centres-villes tout en tenant compte du niveau de vie des familles et en mettant à leur disposition des balcons et des jardins communs conviviaux pourrait constituer une piste de solution. Voilà une tâche dont devrait s\'acquitter l\'architecte du gouvernement de Nouvelle-Galles-du-Sud, dont les activités seraient encadrées par un champ précis.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Over the past decade, our lives have changed through technology, with many working from home, and Sydney has gained an impressive network of metro and light rail systems. Our ability to purchase online has changed the way we shop, and friends and family seem closer because of smartphone communication. All of these adaptations from one system to another can also occur in our built environment through a planning focus on adaptive reuse rather than preferencing heritage preservation.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Au cours de la dernière décennie, la technologie a impacté nos vies à tous, poussant beaucoup à travailler depuis leur domicile ; ainsi la ville de Sydney s\'est dotée d\'un impressionnant réseau de métros et de systèmes ferroviaires légers. La possibilité d\'acheter en ligne a changé notre manière d\'effectuer des achats ; nos amis et les membres de notre famille semblent désormais plus près de nous, du fait de la communication facilitée par le smartphone. Tous ces mécanismes d\'adaptation en passant d\'un système à un autre peuvent également s\'appliquer dans notre système de construction à travers une planification axée sur le recyclage plutôt que sur la préservation de l\'héritage.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Chris Johnson is a former NSW government architect (1995-2005) and executive director, NSW Department of Planning (2005-2009). He was CEO of Urban Taskforce Australia between 2011 and 2019.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Chris Johnson est un ancien architecte du gouvernement de Nouvelle-Galles-du-Sud (1995-2005) et directeur exécutif du département en charge de la planification de la Nouvelle-Galles-du-Sud (2005-2009). Il a occupé le poste de PDG de l\'organisme Urban Taskforce Australia entre 2011 et 2019.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'A final push for female equality', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Un dernier effort en faveur de l\'égalité des genres']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Last year, the World Economic Forum forecast that it would take five generations to achieve gender equality in every nation. Now the World Bank wants to rapidly accelerate that time frame.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['L\'année dernière, les prévisions du Forum économique mondial indiquaient qu\'il faudrait cinq générations pour atteindre l\'égalité des genres dans tous les pays du monde. La Banque mondiale est désormais engagée en vue d\'accélérer la réalisation de cet objectif.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The international financial institution is poised to launch a strategy aimed at significantly advancing the rights and economic opportunities for girls and women by 2030. The plan focuses on improving inclusivity and resilience through access to finance, technological innovation, and changes in public policy and law.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['L\'institution financière mondiale est prête à appliquer une stratégie visant à faire avancer de façon considérable les droits et les possibilités à caractère économique des jeunes filles et des femmes à l\'horizon 2030. Le plan s\'articule autour de l\'amélioration de l\'inclusion et de la résilience par le biais de l\'accès au financement, à l\'innovation technologique et au changement dans le secteur des politiques publiques et du droit.']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"Recent research demonstrates that both social norms and mindsets can change, for example, that engaging men and boys can foster their support and buy-in for gender equality," a consultative draft of the plan states. "Positive gender outcomes can be accelerated and scaled with a better understanding of ... how social norms and mindsets shape everyday expectations, priorities, and practices."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Un projet de plan consultatif souligne que des recherches récentes ont montré que les normes sociales et les paradigmes peuvent changer, par exemple, que des hommes et des jeunes garçons peuvent augmenter leur soutien et s\'engager en faveur de l\'égalité des genres. "Des résultats positifs sur la question du genre  peuvent être obtenus plus rapidement et même accentués, grâce à une meilleure compréhension du  fonctionnement des normes sociales et du paradigme, ainsi que de la manière dont ils façonnent nos attentes, nos priorités et nos habitudes au quotidien".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Shifts in thought are harder to quantify than bank loans for rural women or school enrollment for girls. Yet there is plenty of evidence that female agency can move mountains. In Iran, for example, women have led the greatest threat to the Islamic government in 40 years simply by refusing to comply with laws that force them to cover their hair. In some of the 130 countries with minimum quotas for female representation in government, such as India, male resistance to female voting and political activism has eased.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Un changement de paradigme peut s\'avérer plus difficile à quantifier que des crédits bancaires à destination des femmes rurales ou que le taux de scolarisation des jeunes filles. Toutefois, il ne fait l\'ombre d\'aucun doute que l\'entrain d\'une femme peut déplacer des montagnes. En Iran, par exemple, les femmes ont constitué la plus grande menace du gouvernement islamique des 40 dernières années en refusant de se plier à des lois qui leur imposaient de se couvrir les cheveux. Dans certains des 130 pays enregistrant les quotas de représentativité des femmes au gouvernement les plus bas à l\'instar de l\'Inde, la résistance masculine à l\'égard du vote des femmes et de leur militantisme politique a baissé.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'In some rural African communities, civil society organizations are replacing a harmful rite of passage with health education. One such program helped Kamanda Timayio, leader of the Masai village of Maparasha, Kenya, change his mind about female genital mutilation. He told Le Monde that he had "emerged from ignorance" and would abandon the practice.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Dans certaines communautés rurales d\'Afrique, les organisations de la société civile oeuvrent en vue de remplacer un rite de passage pernicieux par l\'éducation sanitaire. Un tel programme a permis à Kamanda Timayio, chef du village des Masai de Maparasha au Kenya, de changer d\'avis concernant les mutilations génitales féminines. Il a révélé au journal Le Monde qu\'il "est sorti de l\'ignorance" et se sent prêt à abandonner cette pratique.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank cites other examples. From 1970 to 2022, Bangladesh quadrupled female literacy rates and doubled female participation in the labor force. Its gross domestic product more than tripled. The change gathered its own momentum. Recruiting salaried women as teachers and health workers from within their own communities boosted trust "and made women\'s mobility and work more socially acceptable."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['La Banque mondiale cite d\'autres exemples. En effet, de 1970 à 2022, le Bangladesh a quadruplé son taux d\'alphabétisation des femmes et doublé leur participation en qualité de main-d\'oeuvre. Par conséquent, son produit intérieur brut a plus que triplé. Le changement a créé sa propre émulation. Le recrutement de femmes salariées comme enseignantes ou professionnelles de la santé au sein de leurs propres communautés a accentué le climat de confiance "et fait de la mobilité des femmes et de leur accession au travail une réalité plus acceptable aux yeux de la société".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The bank\'s plan would target norms and institutions that may still require generational shifts. It has taken Rwanda more than two decades to establish itself as a model for land reforms that boost economic empowerment for women."No one benefits if women are held back," Rwanda President Paul Kagame said, arguing for land reform in 2015. "We have to change mindsets, not just the laws."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Le plan de la banque ciblera des normes sociales, ainsi que des institutions qui afficheront toujours un besoin de changement générationnel. Il a fallu plus de deux décennies au Rwanda pour se positionner comme un modèle en matière de reformes foncières au service de l\'autonomisation économique des femmes. "Nul ne tire profit du maintien en retrait des femmes", a déclaré le président rwandais Paul Kamage, en faveur de la réforme foncière en 2015. Il rechérit : "nous devons changer de paradigme, pas juste nos lois".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank hopes to spread that message.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['La Banque mondiale espère faire parvenir ce message aux communautés du monde.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'German farmers and train drivers are scaring Germany\'s bosses', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'French', references: ['Les agriculteurs et les conducteurs de trains allemands instillent la peur chez les chefs d\'entreprises']),
];

const List<TranslationSample> enToHi_inDataset = [
  TranslationSample(source: 'Siso\'s depictions of land, water center new gallery exhibition', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['सीसो का ज़मीन, जल का चित्रण नई गैलरी प्रदर्शनी का केन्द्र']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"People Swimming in the Swimming Pool" from 2022 is one Vicente Siso artwork that will display at Tierra del Sol Gallery beginning Jan. 13. (photo courtesy of Vicente Siso)', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['स्विमिंग पूल में तैर रहे लोग विनसेन्ट सीसो की 2022 की एक ऐसी कलाकृति है जिसे टिएरा डेल सोल गैलरी में 13 जनवरी से दिखाया जाएगा। (फ़ोटो के लिए आभार विनसेन्ट सीसो)']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Tierra del Sol is pleased to present "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" at the new gallery location in West Hollywood. Siso has been an artist in the Studio Arts Program since 2012, this marks his debut solo exhibition. Siso was born 1962 in Madrid and raised between Venezuela, Trinidad and Miami; he moved with his family to Southern California in his early 20s.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['टिएरा डेल सोल को वेस्ट हॉलीवुड में नये गैलरी स्थान में "विनसेन्ट सीसो: ज़मीन और पानी की यादें" प्रस्तुत करने में प्रसन्नता हो रही है। सीसो 2012 से स्टूडियो आर्ट्स प्रोग्राम विद्यार्थी रहे हैं, और यह उनकी पहली सोलो प्रदर्शनी है। सीसो का जन्म 1962 में मैड्रिड में हुआ था और वे वेनेज़ुएला, त्रिनिदाद और मियामी में पले बढ़े थे; वे 20 वर्ष की उम्र के आसपास अपने परिवार के साथ सदर्न कैलिफ़ोर्निया में रहने आ गए थे।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Masterfully working across subject matter, Siso has generated a prolific series of landscapes, portraits, and still-life works rendered in either acrylic, pastel, pencil or watercolor. Drawing from family portraits, his own reference photographs, and recollection, his colorful compositions demonstrate his range of interests and skill across media. Siso\'s tropical landscapes and seascapes reflect the geographies of his past, employing rich patterns and incorporating people to make meaningful connections between culture, memory and the environment. Siso titles his artworks in a mix of Spanish and English, signifying the celebrated and integral complexities of his life in Los Angeles County. "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" opens on Saturday, Jan. 13, with a reception from 6-8 p.m. The exhibition is on view through Sunday, March 3.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['कई तरह के विषयों पर कुशलतापूर्वक काम करते हुए, सीसो ने एक्रिलिक, पेस्टल, पेन्सिल या वॉटरकलर में लैंडस्केप, पोर्ट्रेट और स्टिल-लाइफ कलाकृतियों का बहुत बड़ा सीरीज़ उत्पन्न किया है। परिवार के पोर्ट्रेटों, अपने खुद के संदर्भ फोटोग्राफ और याद में से प्रेरणा लेते हुए, उनकी रंगबिरंगी रचनाएं उनकी रुचियों के रेंज और विविध मीडिया में उनके कौशल को दिखाती हैं। सीसो के ऊष्णकटीबंधीय लैंडस्केप और सीस्केप उनके भूतकाल की भूगोल को दिखाते हैं और संस्कृति, याद और पर्यावरण के बीच अर्थपूर्ण जुड़ाव के लिए समृद्ध पैटर्नों का इस्तेमाल करके उनमें लोगों को शामिल करते हैं। सीसो अपनी कलाकृतियों के शीर्षक अंग्रेज़ी और स्पेनिश के मिश्रण में देते हैं, जोकि लॉस एंजलस में उनके जीवन की सुप्रसिद्ध और समेकित जटिलता को चिह्नित करते हैं। "विनसेन्ट सीसो: ज़मीन और पानी की यादें" शनिवार, 13 जनवरी को शुरू हो रहा है, और शाम 6 से 8 बजे तक एक रिसेप्शन होगा। प्रदर्शनी को रविवार 3 मार्च तक देखा जा सकता है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The Tierra del Sol Gallery is located at 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. For information, visit tierradelsolgallery.org.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['टिएरा डेल सोल गैलरी 7414 Santa Monica Blvd पर स्थित है। जानकारी के लिए tierradelsolgallery.org पर जाएं।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Adapt the old, accommodate the new to solve issue', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['समस्या के समाधान के लिए पुराने को अनुकूलित करें, नये की जगह बनाएं']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'At the precinct level, we just need to look at the Sydney CBD as an example of an area which has grown from its pre-settlement landscape into a two-storey city, from a maximum height of 150 feet to the soaring towers of today. At a much scaled-down level, the same can occur across Sydney\'s town centres located around transport nodes. Inner suburbs must also evolve, with a swing to more affordable apartment living at heights below the tree tops on key sites. Of course, the new growth in housing needs to be well-designed and trees, landscaping and parks need to be included along with other essential infrastructure.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['प्रीसिंक्ट स्तर पर हमें बस सिडनी CBD को एक ऐसे इलाके के उदाहरण के रूप में देखना होगा, जो कि अपने उपनिवेश पहले के परिदृश्य से दो मंज़िलों वाले शहर में बढ़ता है, 150 फुट की अधिकतम ऊँचाई से आज के आसमान छूने वाले टावरों तक। एक बहुत घटाए हुए स्तर पर, सिडनी के परिवहन नोड्स के आसपास स्थित टाउन सेंटरों के साथ भी यही हो सकता है। अंदरुनी उपनगर भी विकसित होंगे, जहां मुख्य साइटों पर पेड़ों के सिरों से नीचे की ऊँचाई पर किफायती अपार्टमेन्ट जीवन की ओर झुकाव होगा। बेशक आवास में नयी वृद्धि अच्छी तरह से डिज़ाइन की गई होनी चाहिए, और अन्य आवश्यक सुविधाओं के साथ पेड़, लैंडस्केपिंग और बगीचे शामिल होने चाहिए।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Our planning system also needs to adapt so that planners in suburban councils, who seem to be less supportive of change, are not the only determinants of the future shape of their suburbs. A way forward could be to have an independent decision-making body that championed quality design as long as it fitted below the tree tops and incorporated family living, large balconies, common gardens and presented a friendly appearance. This could be a role for the current NSW government architect working within a carefully crafted complying code.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['हमारी योजना प्रणाली को भी अनुकूल होना होगा ताकि उपनगरीय परिषदों के प्लानर, जो कि परिवर्तन का कम समर्थन कर रहे हों ऐसे लगते हैं, अपने उपनगरों के भावी आकार के एकमात्र निर्धारणकर्ता न हों। आगे बढ़ने का एक तरीका यह हो सकता है कि एक स्वतंत्र निर्णयकर्ता निकाय हो, जो पेड़ों के सिरों के नीचे हो और पारिवारिक जीवन को शामिल करे, बड़ी बाल्कनियाँ हों, साझा बाग हों और दोस्ताना दिखावट वाले हों तब तक अच्छी गुणवत्ता वाले डिज़ाइन का समर्थन करे। यह एक ध्यानपूर्वक बनाई गई अनुपालन संहिता के भीतर काम कर रहे मौजूदा NSW सरकारी आर्किटेक्ट की भूमिका हो सकती है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Over the past decade, our lives have changed through technology, with many working from home, and Sydney has gained an impressive network of metro and light rail systems. Our ability to purchase online has changed the way we shop, and friends and family seem closer because of smartphone communication. All of these adaptations from one system to another can also occur in our built environment through a planning focus on adaptive reuse rather than preferencing heritage preservation.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['पिछले दशक के दौरान, हमारी ज़िंदगियाँ टेक्नोलॉजी के द्वारा बदल गई हैं, कई लोग घर से काम कर रहे हैं, और सिडनी ने मेट्रो और लाइट रेल प्रणालियों का एक प्रभावशाली नेटवर्क हासिल किया है। ऑनलाइन खरीद पाने की हमारी क्षमता ने हमारे खरीदारी के तरीके को बदल दिया है, और दोस्त और रिश्तेदार स्मार्टफोन संचार के कारण और भी करीब लगते हैं। एक प्रणाली में से दूसरी में हुए ये सभी अनुकूलन हमारे निर्मित परिवेश में भी हो सकते हैं, जहाँ विरासत के संरक्षण को वरीयता देने के बजाए, योजना अनुकूलित पुनर्उपयोग पर केन्द्रित हो।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Chris Johnson is a former NSW government architect (1995-2005) and executive director, NSW Department of Planning (2005-2009). He was CEO of Urban Taskforce Australia between 2011 and 2019.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['क्रिस जॉनसन एक भूतपूर्व NSW सरकार आर्किटेक्ट (1995-2005) और, NSW डिपार्टमेन्ट ऑफ प्लानिंग के कार्यकारी निदेशक (2005-2009) हैं। वह 2011 और 2019 के बीच अर्बन टास्कफोर्स ऑस्ट्रेलिया के CEO थे।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'A final push for female equality', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['स्त्री समानता के लिए एक निर्णायक कोशिश']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Last year, the World Economic Forum forecast that it would take five generations to achieve gender equality in every nation. Now the World Bank wants to rapidly accelerate that time frame.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['पिछले साल विश्व आर्थिक फोरम ने पूर्वानुमान लगाया था कि हरेक राष्ट्र में लैंगिक समानता हासिल करने में पाँच पीढ़ियाँ लगेंगी। अब विश्व बैंक उस समय सीमा को तेज़ी से गतिशील करना चाहता है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The international financial institution is poised to launch a strategy aimed at significantly advancing the rights and economic opportunities for girls and women by 2030. The plan focuses on improving inclusivity and resilience through access to finance, technological innovation, and changes in public policy and law.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['यह अंतरराष्ट्रीय वित्तीय संस्थान 2030 तक लड़कियों और महिलाओं के लिए अधिकारों और आर्थिक अवसरों को बहुत उन्नत बनाने के लिए लक्षित एक कार्य नीति लॉन्च करने को तैयार है। यह योजना वित्त, तकनीकी नवोत्पाद और सार्वजनिक नीति और कानून में परिवर्तन के माध्यम से समावेशिता और लचीलेपन को बेहतर बनाने पर केन्द्रित है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"Recent research demonstrates that both social norms and mindsets can change, for example, that engaging men and boys can foster their support and buy-in for gender equality," a consultative draft of the plan states. "Positive gender outcomes can be accelerated and scaled with a better understanding of ... how social norms and mindsets shape everyday expectations, priorities, and practices."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['हाल का शोध दिखाता है कि सामाजिक नियम और सोच, दोनों बदल सकते हैं, उदाहरण के लिए, पुरुषों और लड़कों को शामिल करने से लैंगिक समानता के लिए उनका समर्थन पोषित किया जा सकता है और उन्हें योजना में शामिल किया जा सकता है। योजना का एक परामर्शक मसौदा कहता है "सकारात्मक लैंगिक परिणामों को सामाजिक नियम और सोच किस तरह से रोज़मर्रा की अपेक्षाओं, वरीयताओं और कार्यरीतियों को आकार देते हैं, इसे समझ कर तेज़ किया जा सकता है और नापा जा सकता है।"']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Shifts in thought are harder to quantify than bank loans for rural women or school enrollment for girls. Yet there is plenty of evidence that female agency can move mountains. In Iran, for example, women have led the greatest threat to the Islamic government in 40 years simply by refusing to comply with laws that force them to cover their hair. In some of the 130 countries with minimum quotas for female representation in government, such as India, male resistance to female voting and political activism has eased.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['सोच में परिवर्तनों को ग्रामीण महिलाओं के लिए बैंक ऋण या लड़कियों के लिे स्कूलों में नामांकन की तरह गणनीय रूप देना मुश्किल है। फिर भी इस बात का बहुत साक्ष्य है कि महिलाओं का अधिकार बोध परबतों को हिला सकता है। उदाहरण के लिए, ईरान में महिलाएं केवल उन्हें अपने बालों को ढकने को बाध्य करने वाले कानून का अनुपालन करने से इन्कार करके इस्लामिक सरकार के खिलाफ 40 सालों के सब से बड़े खतरे का नेतृत्व कर रही हैं। भारत जैसे कुछ 130 देश जिनमें सरकार में महिलाओं के प्रतिनिधित्व के लिए न्यूनतम क्वोटा है, महिलाओं द्वारा मतदान और राजनीतिक कार्यकर्ता होने के प्रति पुरुषों का विरोध कम हो गया है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'In some rural African communities, civil society organizations are replacing a harmful rite of passage with health education. One such program helped Kamanda Timayio, leader of the Masai village of Maparasha, Kenya, change his mind about female genital mutilation. He told Le Monde that he had "emerged from ignorance" and would abandon the practice.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['कुछ ग्रामीण आफ्रीकी समुदायों में, नागरिक समाज संस्थान एक नुकसानदेह उत्सव के स्थान पर स्वास्थ्य शिक्षा प्रदान कर रहे हैं। ऐसे एक प्रोग्राम ने मापाराशा, केन्या के मसाई गाँव के नेता कामान्डो तिमायिओ की महिलाओं के जननांगों को काटने के बारे में अपनी राय बदलने में सहायता की। उन्होंने ल मोन्द को बताया कि वह "अज्ञान से उबर आए हैं" और इस रीति को छोड़ देंगे।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank cites other examples. From 1970 to 2022, Bangladesh quadrupled female literacy rates and doubled female participation in the labor force. Its gross domestic product more than tripled. The change gathered its own momentum. Recruiting salaried women as teachers and health workers from within their own communities boosted trust "and made women\'s mobility and work more socially acceptable."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['विश्व बैंक अन्य उदाहरण भी दे रहा है। 1970 से 2022 तक बांग्लादेश में महिलाओं की साक्षरता दर चार गुनी हो गई और श्रम बल में महिलाओं की शामिलगिरी दुगुनी। इसका सकल घरेलु उत्पाद तीन गुना से अधिक बढ़ गया।परिवर्तन ने अपनी खुद की गति पकड़ ली है। अपने ही समुदाय में से महिलाओं को सवेतन शिक्षिकाओं और स्वास्थ्य कर्मियों के रूप में भरती करने से विश्वास को बढ़ावा मिला "और महिलाओं की गतिशीलता और काम को सामाजिक दृष्टि से अधिक स्वीकार्य बन गया।"']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The bank\'s plan would target norms and institutions that may still require generational shifts. It has taken Rwanda more than two decades to establish itself as a model for land reforms that boost economic empowerment for women."No one benefits if women are held back," Rwanda President Paul Kagame said, arguing for land reform in 2015. "We have to change mindsets, not just the laws."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['बैंक की योजना उन नियमों और संस्थानों को लक्षित करेगी जिन में अब भी पीढ़ीगत परिवर्तन आवश्यक हो सकता है। रवान्डा को खुद को महिलाओं के लिए आर्थिक सशक्तिकरण को बढ़ावा देने वाले ज़मीन से जुड़े सुधारों के लिए खुद को आदर्श के रूप में स्थापित करने में दो दशक से अधिक लगे हैं। "अगर महिलाओं को रोका जाए, तो किसी का लाभ नहीं होता है," 2015 में ज़मीन सुधारों के पक्ष में दलील करते हुए रवान्डा के राष्ट्रपति पॉल कागामे न कहा। "हमें सिर्फ कानून नहीं, सोच भी बदलनी होगी।"']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank hopes to spread that message.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['विश्व बैंक इस संदेश को फैलाने की आशा करता है।']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'German farmers and train drivers are scaring Germany\'s bosses', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Hindi', references: ['जर्मन किसान और ट्रेन ड्राइवर जर्मनी के कंपनी मालिकों को डरा रहे हैं']),
];

const List<TranslationSample> enToEs_mxDataset = [
  TranslationSample(source: 'Siso\'s depictions of land, water center new gallery exhibition', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Representaciones de la tierra y el agua de Siso centran una nueva exposición']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"People Swimming in the Swimming Pool" from 2022 is one Vicente Siso artwork that will display at Tierra del Sol Gallery beginning Jan. 13. (photo courtesy of Vicente Siso)', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['"Gente nadando en la alberca" (2022) es una de las obras de Vicente Siso que se expondrán en la galería Tierra del Sol a partir del 13 de enero. (foto cortesía de Vicente Siso)']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Tierra del Sol is pleased to present "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" at the new gallery location in West Hollywood. Siso has been an artist in the Studio Arts Program since 2012, this marks his debut solo exhibition. Siso was born 1962 in Madrid and raised between Venezuela, Trinidad and Miami; he moved with his family to Southern California in his early 20s.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Tierra del Sol se complace en presentar "Vicente Siso: Recuerdos de la tierra y el agua" en la nueva ubicación de esta galería, en West Hollywood. Siso lleva siendo un artista del Studio Arts Program desde 2012, y este evento marca su debut en una exposición en solitario. Siso nació en Madrid en 1962 y se crió entre Venezuela, Trinidad y Miami. A los 20 años se muda con su familia al sur de California.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Masterfully working across subject matter, Siso has generated a prolific series of landscapes, portraits, and still-life works rendered in either acrylic, pastel, pencil or watercolor. Drawing from family portraits, his own reference photographs, and recollection, his colorful compositions demonstrate his range of interests and skill across media. Siso\'s tropical landscapes and seascapes reflect the geographies of his past, employing rich patterns and incorporating people to make meaningful connections between culture, memory and the environment. Siso titles his artworks in a mix of Spanish and English, signifying the celebrated and integral complexities of his life in Los Angeles County. "Vicente Siso: Memories of the Land and Water" opens on Saturday, Jan. 13, with a reception from 6-8 p.m. The exhibition is on view through Sunday, March 3.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Trabajando con maestría diversas temáticas, Siso ha generado una prolífica serie de paisajes, retratos y bodegones realizados en acrílico, pastel, lápiz o acuarela. A partir de retratos familiares, de sus propias fotografías referenciales y de sus recuerdos, sus coloridas composiciones demuestran su amplitud de intereses y su habilidad con los distintos medios. Los paisajes tropicales y marinos de Siso reflejan las geografías de su pasado, empleando ricos patrones e incorporando personas para crear conexiones significativas entre la cultura, la memoria y el medio ambiente. Siso da título a sus obras en una mezcla de español e inglés, evidenciando la notoria complejidad integral de su vida en el condado de Los Ángeles. "Vicente Siso: Recuerdos de la tierra y el agua" abre al público el sábado 13 de enero, con una recepción de 18:00 a 20:00. La exposición permanecerá abierta hasta el domingo 3 de marzo, inclusive.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The Tierra del Sol Gallery is located at 7414 Santa Monica Blvd. For information, visit tierradelsolgallery.org.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['La galería Tierra del Sol se encuentra en el 7414 de Santa Mónica Blvd. Para más información, visita tierradelsolgallery.org.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Adapt the old, accommodate the new to solve issue', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Adapta lo viejo, incorpora lo nuevo para resolver el problema']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'At the precinct level, we just need to look at the Sydney CBD as an example of an area which has grown from its pre-settlement landscape into a two-storey city, from a maximum height of 150 feet to the soaring towers of today. At a much scaled-down level, the same can occur across Sydney\'s town centres located around transport nodes. Inner suburbs must also evolve, with a swing to more affordable apartment living at heights below the tree tops on key sites. Of course, the new growth in housing needs to be well-designed and trees, landscaping and parks need to be included along with other essential infrastructure.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['A nivel de área llega con fijarnos en el centro de negocios de Sídney como ejemplo de zona que ha crecido desde su paisaje previo a la colonización hasta convertirse en una ciudad de dos alturas, desde una altura máxima de 45 metros hasta las altísimas torres de hoy en día. A una escala mucho más reducida, lo mismo puede ocurrir en los centros urbanos de Sídney situados en torno a nodos de transporte. Los suburbios interiores también tienen que evolucionar, con una tendencia hacia viviendas más asequibles con alturas por debajo de las copas de los árboles en lugares clave. Obviamente, el nuevo crecimiento habitacional debe estar bien diseñado y debe incluir árboles, parques y jardines, así como otras infraestructuras esenciales.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Our planning system also needs to adapt so that planners in suburban councils, who seem to be less supportive of change, are not the only determinants of the future shape of their suburbs. A way forward could be to have an independent decision-making body that championed quality design as long as it fitted below the tree tops and incorporated family living, large balconies, common gardens and presented a friendly appearance. This could be a role for the current NSW government architect working within a carefully crafted complying code.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Nuestro sistema de planeamiento también debe adaptarse para que los planificadores de los municipios suburbanos (que parecen menos dispuestos al cambio) no sean los únicos en determinar la forma que tomarán sus suburbios en el futuro. Una forma de seguir adelante podría ser contar con un organismo independiente de toma de decisiones que defendiera un diseño de calidad, siempre que cupiera por debajo de las copas de los árboles e incorporara la vida en familia, así como amplios balcones, jardines comunitarios, y presentara un aspecto amable. Este podría ser un papel para el actual arquitecto del Gobierno de Nueva Gales del Sur, trabajando dentro de los márgenes de un código de cumplimiento cuidadosamente elaborado.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Over the past decade, our lives have changed through technology, with many working from home, and Sydney has gained an impressive network of metro and light rail systems. Our ability to purchase online has changed the way we shop, and friends and family seem closer because of smartphone communication. All of these adaptations from one system to another can also occur in our built environment through a planning focus on adaptive reuse rather than preferencing heritage preservation.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['A lo largo de la pasada década nuestras vidas han cambiado gracias a la tecnología, donde muchos trabajan desde casa, y Sídney se ha dotado de una impresionante red de metro y tren ligero. El poder comprar por Internet ha cambiado, precisamente, nuestra forma de comprar, y los amigos y la familia parecen estar más cerca gracias a la comunicación vía smartphone. Todas estas adaptaciones de un sistema a otro pueden producirse, también, en nuestro entorno construido a través de una planificación centrada en la reutilización adaptativa, en vez de dar preferencia a la conservación del patrimonio.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Chris Johnson is a former NSW government architect (1995-2005) and executive director, NSW Department of Planning (2005-2009). He was CEO of Urban Taskforce Australia between 2011 and 2019.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Chris Johnson es un antiguo arquitecto del Gobierno de Nueva Gales del Sur (1995-2005) y director ejecutivo del Departamento de Planificación de Nueva Gales del Sur (2005-2009). Fue director ejecutivo del Urban Taskforce Australia entre 2011 y 2019.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'A final push for female equality', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Un último empujón por la igualdad femenina']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Last year, the World Economic Forum forecast that it would take five generations to achieve gender equality in every nation. Now the World Bank wants to rapidly accelerate that time frame.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['El año pasado, el Foro Económico Mundial pronosticó que harían falta cinco generaciones para lograr la igualdad de género en todas las naciones. Ahora, el Banco Mundial quiere acelerar ese plazo rápidamente.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The international financial institution is poised to launch a strategy aimed at significantly advancing the rights and economic opportunities for girls and women by 2030. The plan focuses on improving inclusivity and resilience through access to finance, technological innovation, and changes in public policy and law.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['La institución financiera internacional está preparada para lanzar una estrategia destinada a promover de forma significativa los derechos y las oportunidades económicas de niñas y mujeres para 2030. El plan se centra en mejorar la inclusión y la resiliencia a través del acceso a la financiación, la innovación tecnológica y los cambios en la legislación y políticas públicas.']),
  TranslationSample(source: '"Recent research demonstrates that both social norms and mindsets can change, for example, that engaging men and boys can foster their support and buy-in for gender equality," a consultative draft of the plan states. "Positive gender outcomes can be accelerated and scaled with a better understanding of ... how social norms and mindsets shape everyday expectations, priorities, and practices."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['"Investigaciones recientes demuestran que tanto las normas sociales como las mentalidades pueden cambiar; por ejemplo, que el involucrar a hombres y niños puede fomentar su apoyo y aceptación de la igualdad de género", afirma un borrador consultivo del plan. "Los resultados positivos en materia de género pueden acelerarse y ampliarse con una mayor comprensión de ... cómo las normas sociales y la mentalidad determinan las expectativas, prioridades y prácticas cotidianas".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'Shifts in thought are harder to quantify than bank loans for rural women or school enrollment for girls. Yet there is plenty of evidence that female agency can move mountains. In Iran, for example, women have led the greatest threat to the Islamic government in 40 years simply by refusing to comply with laws that force them to cover their hair. In some of the 130 countries with minimum quotas for female representation in government, such as India, male resistance to female voting and political activism has eased.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Los cambios de mentalidad son más complicados de cuantificar que los préstamos bancarios a las mujeres rurales, o la escolarización de las niñas. Aún así, hay evidencias de sobra de que la acción femenina puede mover montañas. En Irán, por ejemplo, las mujeres han liderado la mayor amenaza al gobierno islámico en 40 años con simplemente negarse a cumplir las leyes que las obligan a cubrirse el cabello. En algunos de los 130 países con cuotas mínimas de representación femenina en el gobierno, como la India, la resistencia masculina al voto femenino y al activismo político ha disminuido.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'In some rural African communities, civil society organizations are replacing a harmful rite of passage with health education. One such program helped Kamanda Timayio, leader of the Masai village of Maparasha, Kenya, change his mind about female genital mutilation. He told Le Monde that he had "emerged from ignorance" and would abandon the practice.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['En algunas comunidades rurales de África, las organizaciones de la sociedad civil están sustituyendo un dañino rito de iniciación por educación sanitaria. Uno de estos programas ayudó a Kamanda Timayio, líder de la aldea masai de Maparasha (Kenia), a cambiar de opinión sobre la mutilación genital femenina. Declaró a Le Monde que había "dejado atrás la ignorancia" y que abandonaría esa práctica.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank cites other examples. From 1970 to 2022, Bangladesh quadrupled female literacy rates and doubled female participation in the labor force. Its gross domestic product more than tripled. The change gathered its own momentum. Recruiting salaried women as teachers and health workers from within their own communities boosted trust "and made women\'s mobility and work more socially acceptable."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['El Banco Mundial cita otros ejemplos. De 1970 a 2022, Bangladesh cuadruplicó las tasas de alfabetización femenina y duplicó la participación femenina en la población activa. Su producto interior bruto se triplicó con creces. El cambio cobró su propio impulso. La contratación de mujeres asalariadas como maestras y trabajadoras sanitarias dentro de sus propias comunidades impulsó la confianza "e hizo que la movilidad y el trabajo de las mujeres fueran más aceptables socialmente".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The bank\'s plan would target norms and institutions that may still require generational shifts. It has taken Rwanda more than two decades to establish itself as a model for land reforms that boost economic empowerment for women."No one benefits if women are held back," Rwanda President Paul Kagame said, arguing for land reform in 2015. "We have to change mindsets, not just the laws."', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['El plan del banco se quiere centrar en normas e instituciones que todavía puedan requerir cambios generacionales. A Ruanda le ha tomado más de dos décadas establecerse como modelo de reforma agraria que impulsa el empoderamiento económico de las mujeres: "Nadie se beneficia si se reprime a las mujeres", dijo el presidente de Ruanda, Paul Kagame, defendiendo la reforma agraria en 2015. "Tenemos que cambiar la mentalidad, no sólo las leyes".']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'The World Bank hopes to spread that message.', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['El Banco Mundial espera difundir ese mensaje.']),
  TranslationSample(source: 'German farmers and train drivers are scaring Germany\'s bosses', language: 'English', convLanguage: 'Spanish', references: ['Agricultores, ganaderos y maquinistas de Alemania asustan a la patronal']),
